<p>Social media for accountants is not about going viral. It is about being visible to the right 200-500 business owners in your local market when they need financial help. Post consistently. Share expertise. Let the trust compound over time. The firms that show up on LinkedIn every week get the referrals and the search traffic that invisible firms do not.</p>
